org.zoolu.sip.address

Class SipURL

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zoolu.sip.address.SipURL

  • public class SipURL
extends java.lang.Object

    Class SipURL implements SIP URLs.

    A SIP URL is a string of the form of: 

     &nbsp&nbsp sip:[user@]hostname[:port][;parameters]

    If port number is ommitted, -1 is returned
